
------ ADMIN CONSOLE -------

(Step One) Log in as System Admin.

(Step Two) Within the Application Navigator, search "Scheduled Jobs" under the "System Scheduler" Module.

(Step Three) Click on "New."

(Step Four) Select "Automate the generation and distribution of a report."

(Step Five) Fill out the fields accordingly.

(Step Six) Submit!

**NOTE: The "Report" is the same report generated by the steps in the "Viewing Reports on Tasks as Admin." **
